      "epCost": 1,
      "description": "The Brood Brothers’ keen eyes pick out encroaching foes and mark them for annihilation. STRATEGIC GAMBIT. Select one enemy operative visible to a friendly BROOD BROTHER operative to gain one of your Crossfire tokens. NOTES:",
      "restrictions": null
    }
  ]
